### 2. Login (Get Token)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "pastor@church.com",
  "password": "securepassword123"
}

### 3. Create an Event
POST http://localhost:3000/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Sunday Service",
  "description": "Join us for worship and the word.",
  "startTime": "2026-01-11T10:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2026-01-11T12:00:00Z",
  "location": "Main Sanctuary"
}

### 4. Get All Events
GET http://localhost:3000/events

### 5. Create a Tag
POST http://localhost:3000/tags
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Worship Team",
  "color": "#FF5733"
}

### 6. Assign User to Tag
# REPLACE THE IDs BELOW with real IDs from your previous responses!
# Tag ID comes from the response of request #5
# User ID comes from the response of request #2 (Login)
POST http://localhost:3000/tags/REPLACE_WITH_TAG_ID/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "REPLACE_WITH_USER_ID"
}

### 7. Initiate a Guest Donation
POST http://localhost:3000/donations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 50
}

